## 주요 데이터 모델

### Popup (팝업스토어)
- id, title, brand, category, images[], description
- location: { address, lat, lng, region }
- period: { start, end }
- hours, website, instagram
- likes, commentCount, reportCount, status
- createdBy, createdAt, updatedAt

### User (사용자)
- id, email, password, nickname, profileImage
- role: 'user' | 'business' | 'admin'
- businessInfo?: { businessNumber, companyName, verificationStatus }
- favorites[], notifications

### Comment, Report, Notice, Inquiry
- 각 모델의 상세 스펙은 docs/PROJECT_SPEC.md 참조

